<s> pulling off a gitxsan @-@ gitanyow negotiator and moving him to the nisga'a and putting in sections 33 , 34 and 35 may not be a prejudice , but it is the appearance of prejudice that is damning . </s>
<s> in fact , the gitanyow and gitxsan felt they had been prejudiced . </s>
