<s> honourable senators , let me be as clear as i possibly can be . </s>
<s> the government , after a long period of negotiation with all the parties , accepted the claims of the nisga'a with respect to the boundaries and the use of lands and proceeded to conclude an agreement with the nisga'a . </s>
<s> the treaty and the agreement will be adjusted to the establishment , through negotiation or through litigation , of gitxsan and gitanyow rights . </s>
<s> nothing is shut off ; nothing is closed out . </s>
<s> those rights and the status quo are preserved . </s>
<s> senator lynch @-@ staunton : </s>
<s> how can the government reconcile this pathetic generosity after having clamped down on the two claiming nations ? </s>
