<s> it is solvable . </s>
<s> hon. jerahmiel s. grafstein : </s>
<s> honourable senators , i listened with great care to senator kinsella . </s>
<s> i congratulate him on his ability to set out these issues from his perspective . </s>
<s> he has two constitutional objections , as i hear them . </s>
<s> one is the diminution of the power of the senate , which has been echoed by senator beaudoin , based on the constitution and the conventions of the constitution . </s>
<s> i will not comment on that issue at this time , but i am interested in the senator 's first proposition , which is the ultra vires nature of the legislation . </s>
