<s> i sense a certain restlessness in the house , and perhaps the latter interpretation would be the better approach . </s>
<s> shall we allow senator andreychuk to complete her remarks ? </s>
<s> hon. noël a. kinsella ( deputy leader of the opposition ) : </s>
